# Main Terraform configuration for DevOps Capstone project
# 
# This file serves as the entry point for the Terraform configuration.
# Individual resources are organized in separate files:
#   - providers.tf  : AWS provider and backend configuration
#   - variables.tf  : Input variable definitions
#   - vpc.tf        : VPC and networking resources
#   - ecr.tf        : Container registry resources
#   - outputs.tf    : Output value definitions
